            - **parts** draw components of PDF. Default False.

        **Returns**
        
        ((data_x, datay), (errorp,errorm), (total_pdf_x, total_pdf_y), parts)
        """
        return plotting.draw_x2(self, minuit=minuit, ax=ax, parmloc=parmloc,
